    "emoji": "9️⃣",
    "ideation": "The number nine is the final single digit—the peak of the sequence before it rolls over. To personify this, I am treating the face as a 'countdown reaching its limit.' The eyes act as mechanical tally wheels, spinning vertically (gaze_y) to simulate the rolling of a counter. The mouth represents the tension of a spring-loaded mechanism about to snap. The color shifts from a cool 'operating' blue to a high-alert gold as we reach the maximum digit. The animation arc moves from the readiness of '8 turning to 9' to the final, satisfied click of the number locking into place at its maximum value.",
